text: Khanadelwal mera bhai..college ka sabse bada chaapu ğŸ˜, tumse bada inspiration sahayd he koi ho. Hustle kya hota hai tumse sikha,  Hum dono ko civil pasande nahi tha ğŸ˜‚, first year me baap ke samne kitne masti karte the aapan...fest ke masti ya first year me TA ke copy sab ek sath karte the, (Treasure Hunt) Hall 1 me jab tu nikla tha bahana maar ke voh kabhi nahi bhulunga ğŸ˜‚, ya orientation ke time apan jab stage me jaane se chuupte the, Voh bhi kya din the. text: Rajput!(the gem) kya hall chaalğŸ˜. Pata nahi apan dost kaise bane, different hall different friend group, but i guess dep. se tuning match hui ğŸ˜ƒ. Second year me mile the fir roz milne laggaye classes ya labs ke liye , thanks for making acads easy. MT ke chai ho ya lib. ,RM be maggai, tere me humesha ek positve aura dekha hai jo har problem solve karde haste haste, you are a shining star my friend I hope we always stay connected. author: Aaiyush  Kapurwan

text: Deepak, Mere bhai mere roome mere dost kaam more like a real Brother, maine jab tumhe itne passion se game khelte dekhta tabhi soch liya ke apan he roommates banenge, tum humesha ek unsolved mystery rahe jisko solve karna bohot mushkil tha, kyuki tume kholna bohot muskil tha, maybe in the end I succeded ğŸ˜‚. Apan ne sath me CPI girayi aur uthai hai, alag alag reasons se. Sorry jab jab tu kuch sunata tha mai beech me tookta tha ğŸ˜‚ I enjoyed doing that. Maine kafi try kiya ke apne thode jhagde ho aur maza aaye but u were always the peacekeeper. Apan sab share karte the aur girls kpop toh alag he ğŸ˜‚. Kitne kathi me raid mare hai, aur jaise he kuch mast milte tha internet me share karte the.  I know you are not very social but stay in touch. You will always be my brother.
author: Aaiyush  Kapurwan

text: Dinesh, mera bhai mera dost mere wingi ğŸ˜œ,starting se end tak aapan kafi backchod dost rahe, fest ke masti ya pure wing ke GPL me apna participation humesh rehta thağŸ˜, Udghosh ke ShowM me kya bachkchodi kari thi aapan ne, seniors ke kitni maari thi ğŸ˜‚, inhone humesha party ke liye maana kara but humne koshish nahi chodi, maybe aage tumhe mana lenge. DS ke copy ya bakiyo ke biching karna apna bulla session epic hota tha ğŸ˜‚, yeh sala bahar se jitna saakth londa ho utna he aandar se sacha dost hai, Ab sale NRI hoke bhool mat jaana yaado me rakhna dil me basa ke rehna. Your close Friend (Saccha Bhai) -Aaiyush .
author: Aaiyush  Kapurwan
